This is The PHP API Wrapper for the mchoice-aventura 
which is underline platform behind appzone.lk

Author: Arunoda Susiripala <arunoda.susiripala@gmail.com>

This api contains two major classes
* AppZoneSender
* AppZoneReciever

which does sending and recieving SMS.

And you can have a look at samples

* sending sms -> sample/send.php
* recieving sms and sending back -> sample/recieve.php


